{
  "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.64,
      "size": 26208,
      "text": "夜空中的行星，年复一年地绕着太阳旋转。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.3,
      "size": 36864,
      "text": "四百年前，开普勒盯着火星的观测数据，想找出它运行的规律。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "他发现，行星的轨道不是正圆，而是一个椭圆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "orbit",
      "line_id": "orbit-1",
      "filename": "orbit-orbit-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/orbit-orbit-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39600,
      "text": "椭圆有两个焦点，而太阳并不在中心，它恰好待在其中一个焦点上。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "orbit",
      "line_id": "orbit-2",
      "filename": "orbit-orbit-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/orbit-orbit-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.57,
      "size": 41184,
      "text": "于是行星离太阳时近时远：最近处叫近日点，最远处叫远日点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "orbit",
      "line_id": "orbit-3",
      "filename": "orbit-orbit-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/orbit-orbit-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "椭圆越扁，也就是离心率越大，这种远近的差别就越明显。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "area",
      "line_id": "area-1",
      "filename": "area-area-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/area-area-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.62,
      "size": 41904,
      "text": "开普勒第二定律说：行星与太阳的连线，在相等时间里扫过相等的面积。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "area",
      "line_id": "area-2",
      "filename": "area-area-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/area-area-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.46,
      "size": 39312,
      "text": "所以在近日点，行星必须跑得快，才能在短弧上扫出同样大的扇形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "area",
      "line_id": "area-3",
      "filename": "area-area-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/area-area-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.62,
      "size": 25920,
      "text": "而在远日点，它便慢悠悠地掠过长长的弧。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "equation",
      "line_id": "eq-1",
      "filename": "equation-eq-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/equation-eq-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.53,
      "size": 40464,
      "text": "要算出某一时刻行星在哪，得解开普勒方程：M 等于 E 减去 e 乘以 sinE。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "equation",
      "line_id": "eq-2",
      "filename": "equation-eq-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/equation-eq-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "这里 M 随时间均匀增长，而 E 是偏近点角，藏在方程里解不开。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "equation",
      "line_id": "eq-3",
      "filename": "equation-eq-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/equation-eq-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "我们用牛顿迭代法，一步步逼近 E，几次就能收敛到很高精度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "调整离心率，看轨道从近乎正圆，慢慢被拉成瘦长的椭圆。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39744,
      "text": "注意那些彩色扇形，面积始终相等，而行星的快慢却在悄悄变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "行星沿椭圆绕日，太阳稳坐在一个焦点上。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "等时扫过等面积，让近日点飞快、远日点从容。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "kepler-orbit",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/kepler-orbit/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "一条开普勒方程，把天体运行算得明明白白，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 37.13,
  "total_size": 594000
}